Daudi olemo ni Solomon


1  Kane Daudi chiegni tho, nolemo ni Solomon wuode niya, 
2  “An to eri adhi kuma ji duto mae piny dhiye; in to bed motegno kinyiso ni in dichwo. 
3  Mak chik Ruoth Nyasaye ma Nyasachi, kiwuotho e yorene, kendo kimako wechene, gi chikene kod buchene, kaka ondiki e chik Musa, kamoro amora midhiye. 
4  Kamano Ruoth Nyasaye nochopo singruok mane otimona, kowachona ni, ‘Ka yawuoti noritre, kendo nowuoth e nyima gi adiera gi chunygi duto kod parogi duto, to nyikwayi nobed ruodhi mag Israel nyaka chieng’.’


5  

“Bende ing’eyo gima Joab wuod zeruya notimona. Ne onego Abner wuod Ner, kod amasa wuod Jether, mane jotend jolwenj Israel. E ndalo kue, nochulo kuor kuom gima notimore e lweny, kokelona buch remo nikech tho mar ng’at makare. 
6  Omiyo ti gi riekoni; wiye oseti lwar, to kik iwe otho gi kue. 
7  

To tim maber ni jood Barzilai ja-Gilead, kendo ikonygi, nikech ne girwaka gi ng’wono kane aringo Absalom owadu. 
8  

To kik wiyi wil gii Shimei wuod Gera ma ja-Benjamin moa Bahurim, nikech nokuong’a gi kuong’a malit, chieng’ mane awuok kadhi Mahanaim. To bang’, kane romona e aora Jordan, nakuong’orane gi nying Ruoth Nyasaye ni ok nanege. 
9  To koro kik iweye mak ikume. In ng’at mariek, kendo ibiro ng’eyo ng’ama owinjore itim, mondo otho tho mar masira, kata obedo ni wiye oseti lwar kamano.”

